message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech separation, which is a subfield of speech processing. cs.CL is also likely as the paper involves deep learning-based speech separation systems. cs.SI is another possible category as the paper deals with signal processing. cs.LG is also possible as the paper involves machine learning techniques. cs.SY is less likely as the paper does not deal with control systems or robotics.
